## рџ”Ќ Key Insights

- Sales department experienced the highest employee attrition.
- Employees working overtime showed higher resignation rates.
- Employees with lower monthly income had higher turnover.
- Most employees resigned within the first few years of joining.
- Job satisfaction and work-life balance had a significant impact on employee retention.

