## рџљЂ How to Run

### Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/bibi-zainab/HR-Analytics-Dashboard.git
```

### Navigate to the Project Folder

```bash
cd HR-Analytics-Dashboard
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### Run Python Scripts

Execute the analysis scripts or open the Jupyter notebook to explore the data.

